## ðŸ“Œ Key Finding

- Identified **\$263K+** in spend across **underperforming TOF channels** (ROI < 2).
- Theoretical maximum incremental revenue if reallocated to higher-performing channels (ROI ~9) â‰ˆ **\$2.2M**.
- After applying **marginal diminishing returns** and a **conservative 15â€“20% realization factor**, the **realistic uplift** is estimated at **\$165Kâ€“\$221K**, representing a **~104% uplift for this block**.
- This scenario demonstrates how MMM can replace unreliable MTA for TOF channels and support smarter spend reallocation.

